*[[User:Xantji|Xantji]] - fixed some mistakes in [[inputs]].
*[[User:Tchernobill|Tchernobill]] - added explanation about activating mods from the [[Mods#Changing mods in the main menu|main menu]].
*[[User:ChuckleberryFinn|Chuck]] - added more technical details on his [[PZ Reupload Check]] tool.
*[[User:AlexeyMin|AlexeyMin]] - documented how to add loot to zombie corpses during [[OnZombieDead]].
*[[User:Xhr1s|Xhr1s]] and [[User:Curiousbookshelf|Curiousbookshelf]] - fixed some small mistakes in [[Modding]].
*[[User:Chepchel|Chepchel]] - fixed some spelling here and there.
